gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.data

Class Spectrogram

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.core.data.Spectrogram

  • public class Spectrogram
extends Object
    An immutable class for calculating spectrograms. User defines bin size, fft length, and amount of overlap. The signal is windowed using a Kaiser window with user specifiable beta-value.
    Author:
    Peter Cervelli
